{"tid":495104,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[求推介]強調輔助型角色既作品","createTime":"2017-12-10T11:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T12:30:57.000Z","uid":26651,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"cd31266bdb35a235a86d94de8aff0b3e9709e3f5","tid":495104,"uid":26651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"想搵D作品係講主角點樣幫其他人變強。<br />\n主角自身能力可以好強或者好弱，但係開發人地能力方面就超強既角色。<br />\n<br />\n舉幾個例:<br />\n魔法科高校的劣等生(九校戰篇)<br />\n[達也: 幫隊友開發神CAD，有達也做工程師既隊友都榜上有名]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nijimen.net/uploads/topic/wide_image/2990/thumb_3ece4527-7268-488d-80a7-8be535f61d0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nijimen.net%2Fuploads%2Ftopic%2Fwide_image%2F2990%2Fthumb_3ece4527-7268-488d-80a7-8be535f61d0b.jpg&h=7ab5ff17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不正經的魔術講師與禁忌教典<br />\n[葛倫: 極度熟悉魔術原理，以簡單易明既方法教導學生，有佢指揮下，好多平庸既學生都有一定程度既表現]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://anikiji.com/img/article/8474aef0dbd04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fanikiji.com%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F8474aef0dbd04.jpg&h=e7c37a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFate系列 <br />\n[孔明: 自身作為魔術師既能力好有限，但經佢教導過既學生都非常優秀]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201506/237a35640585912a5402af6d0878e239.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201506%2F237a35640585912a5402af6d0878e239.JPG&h=2e79d18c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位有冇好推介? 不論動/漫畫/小說都可以<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66b749c50c469e043040e0a4b74ade36eebcb8f","tid":495104,"uid":34676,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:44:01.000Z","msg":"記錄的地平線<br />\n主角係食腦軍師，負責落buff<br />\n主要戰力都係身邊既團友"},{"pid":"ab7d0528d2b56435e8b7aa2d468ebb831a4cd484","tid":495104,"uid":55511,"lik